01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef, Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 \u0111ang l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng\/ c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ti\u1ebfng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\">Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 t\u00e2m v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh d\u1ea1y theo \u0111\u00fang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a ra.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n r\u00f5 h\u01a1n, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Hotline <span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0987.005.996<\/span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\">Ho\u1eb7c Qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y!<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-shortcode\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;3276&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;shortcode&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (8 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Gia s\